# Enterprise RAG Searcher Project Overview

This project implements an **Enterprise-Ready Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) Searcher** with chatbot capabilities and intelligent agents. The complete requirements are documented in [PRD.md](mdc:docs/PRD.md).

## Core Purpose
- Ingest and index multiple data sources (files, websites, APIs)
- Provide conversational chatbot interface for querying indexed content
- Intelligently route queries using agent-based classification
- Generate precise answers using RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)

## Target Users
- Enterprise support teams
- Software engineers and QA teams
- Product managers
- General enterprise users for self-service knowledge retrieval

## Key Capabilities
- **Data Ingestion**: Files (PDF, DOCX, code), web crawling, API connectors
- **Conversational Interface**: Multi-modal input, contextual awareness, rich responses
- **Intelligent Routing**: Intent classification, specialized workflows for bugs/features/training
- **RAG Processing**: Vector embeddings, hybrid search, schema-aware retrieval
- **Enterprise Features**: RBAC, audit logging, compliance, scalability

## Architecture Layers
1. **Ingestion Layer**: File services, API integrations, web crawlers
2. **Indexing & Search**: Vector databases, embedding models, schema parsers
3. **Query Processing**: Classification agents, RAG handlers, context management
4. **User Interface**: Web chat UI, Slack/Teams bots, admin dashboard
5. **Infrastructure**: Kubernetes deployment, security, monitoring
